---
const trustTags = [
  "Favorito entre huéspedes",
  "Top 10% mejor valoradas",
  "Ubicación 5,0",
  "76 reseñas reales"
];
---

<section class="trust-block" id="confianza">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="trust-shell">
      <div class="trust-main">
        <div class="trust-score-wrap">
          <span class="trust-laurel">✦</span>
          <div class="trust-score">4,95</div>
          <span class="trust-laurel">✦</span>
        </div>

        <p class="trust-kicker">Valoración destacada</p>
        <h2>Una casa elegida una y otra vez por su ubicación, comodidad y atención.</h2>
        <p class="trust-copy">
          Quienes ya se hospedaron destacan la experiencia completa: frente al parque, espacios amplios,
          exterior disfrutable y una atención que transmite confianza desde el primer contacto.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-side">
        <div class="trust-grid">
          <article class="trust-metric">
            <strong>4,95</strong>
            <span>calificación promedio</span>
          </article>

          <article class="trust-metric">
            <strong>76</strong>
            <span>reseñas verificadas</span>
          </article>

          <article class="trust-metric">
            <strong>5,0</strong>
            <span>ubicación</span>
          </article>

          <article class="trust-metric">
            <strong>4,9</strong>
            <span>comunicación</span>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="trust-tags">
          {trustTags.map((tag) => <span>{tag}</span>)}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .trust-block {
    padding: 1.25rem 0 0;
  }

  .trust-shell {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(124, 31, 63, .10), transparent 38%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.82), rgba(255,255,255,.62));
    border: 1px solid rgba(80, 40, 50, .08);
    border-radius: 28px;
    padding: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(30, 20, 25, .06);
  }

  .trust-main h2 {
    margin: .35rem 0 .55rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3.1rem);
    line-height: .95;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .trust-score-wrap {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .7rem;
    margin-bottom: .5rem;
  }

  .trust-score {
    font-size: clamp(2.7rem, 8vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
    color: #2b1b21;
  }

  .trust-laurel {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    color: #a67c2e;
    opacity: .95;
  }

  .trust-kicker {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: .76rem;
    letter-spacing: .14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #7a5a63;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .trust-copy {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 58ch;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #5f5258;
  }

  .trust-side {
    display: grid;
    gap: .85rem;
  }

  .trust-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: .75rem;
  }

  .trust-metric {
    padding: .95rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.78);
    border: 1px solid rgba(80, 40, 50, .08);
  }

  .trust-metric strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: #2b1b21;
  }

  .trust-metric span {
    display: block;
    margin-top: .35rem;
    font-size: .92rem;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: #6a5d63;
  }

  .trust-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: .55rem;
  }

  .trust-tags span {
    padding: .62rem .82rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(80, 40, 50, .08);
    font-size: .86rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: #5c4b52;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .trust-shell {
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr .9fr;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.35rem;
    }
  }
</style>
